<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الإِْشْهَادُ عَلَى طَلَبِ الْمُوَاثَبَةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٦ - اخْتَلَفَ الْفُقَهَاءُ فِي أَنَّ الإِْشْهَادَ عَلَى طَلَبِ الْمُوَاثَبَةِ هُوَ شَرْطُ صِحَّةٍ لَهَا أَوْ هُوَ لإِِثْبَاتِ الْحَقِّ عِنْدَ الْخُصُومَةِ عَلَى تَقْدِيرِ الإِْنْكَارِ؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>انْظُرْ تَفْصِيل ذَلِكَ فِي مُصْطَلَحِ <span class="c2">(شُفْعَةٌ ف ٣٣)</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مُوَادَعَةٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> هُدْنَةٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>مَوَارِيثُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> إِرْثٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>